    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "fa0bb88c_076ea299",
        "filename": "golden/go/tracestore/bt_tracestore/BIGTABLE.md",
        "patchSetId": 13
      },
      "lineNbr": 47,
      "author": {
        "id": 5120
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-05-20T21:44:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t think this is accurate. BT supports column filters to fetch only the columns you want.\nhttps://godoc.org/cloud.google.com/go/bigtable#ColumnFilter\nhttps://godoc.org/cloud.google.com/go/bigtable#ColumnRangeFilter\nhttps://godoc.org/cloud.google.com/go/bigtable#FamilyFilter\n\n(It\u0027s possible that the tablet server will read the entire row from disk, but it won\u0027t return the entire row in the RPC response.)\n\nAssuming a ColumnRangeFilter is reasonably efficient, we could store digests for 11 billion commits in a single row, by my calculations, with the ability to query for any range of commits.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 46,
        "startChar": 51,
        "endLine": 47,
        "endChar": 13
      },
      "revId": "cecf8a2707c82dfaacceb1f212496238f1605937",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "3339c020_ccba59d4",
        "filename": "golden/go/tracestore/bt_tracestore/BIGTABLE.md",
        "patchSetId": 13
      },
      "lineNbr": 47,
      "author": {
        "id": 5395
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-05-22T01:11:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m aware of the family filter (I didn\u0027t mention it here for brevity, one can only have ~100 column families per table), but I was not aware of those other two. My impression though is what you pointed out, we might have to fetch the whole row and then filter the columns.\n\nSmaller rows are better:\nhttps://cloud.google.com/bigtable/docs/performance#slower-perf\n\nJoe knows more about BT than I do, so we could ask him",
      "parentUuid": "fa0bb88c_076ea299",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 46,
        "startChar": 51,
        "endLine": 47,
        "endChar": 13
      },
      "revId": "cecf8a2707c82dfaacceb1f212496238f1605937",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
    },
