      "writtenOn": "2019-05-21T19:02:05Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "In the current ingestion code, there is a distinction between the trace id and the trace params. E.g. in idAndParams (https://skia.googlesource.com/buildbot/+/3ddff862228b8a495d878819dfb64b3ab01f102b/golden/go/goldingestion/common.go#18), the trace id does not include \"Options\" but the trace params do.\n\nIs that distinction still relevant? How is it used? How does this interface handle Options?",
